00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:11.360
&gt;&gt; BARD Express: Browsing
the Recently Added

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:14.470
and Most Popular Lists.

00:00:14.470 --> 00:00:20.710
&gt;&gt; Judy: Hi, I'm Judy Dixon,
Consumer Relations Officer at NLS.

00:00:20.710 --> 00:00:24.320
In this edition of the
BARD Express How-To Series,

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:27.250
I'm going to cover browsing
the BARD most popular

00:00:27.250 --> 00:00:30.310
and recently added lists.

00:00:30.310 --> 00:00:34.930
To browse the recently added
list, select Recently Added Books

00:00:34.930 --> 00:00:38.380
and Magazines from the
BARD Express Main Menu.

00:00:38.380 --> 00:00:42.460
You will be presented with a
list of books and magazines added

00:00:42.460 --> 00:00:45.360
to BARD in the last 10 days.

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:50.350
If you want to display materials
added in the last 30 days, 45 days,

00:00:50.350 --> 00:00:54.590
or 1 day, tab to the
time range combo box

00:00:54.590 --> 00:00:57.250
and select the desired time.

00:00:57.250 --> 00:01:01.510
You can also narrow your results
by using the subject filter.

00:01:01.510 --> 00:01:05.650
In this example I am going to
uncheck all available subjects

00:01:05.650 --> 00:01:11.450
and check the boxes associated
with Adventure and Bestsellers.

00:01:11.450 --> 00:01:16.000
&gt;&gt; NVDA: Loading Recently Added
Books and Magazines Page 1.

00:01:17.530 --> 00:01:23.230
Loaded Recently Added Books
and Magazines items 1 to 45.

00:01:23.230 --> 00:01:24.530
Numbered account.

00:01:24.530 --> 00:01:26.610
Author Reich, Christopher.

00:01:26.610 --> 00:01:28.920
1 of 45.

00:01:28.920 --> 00:01:31.880
&gt;&gt; Judy: Tab to access
the list of titles

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:35.190
and use the arrow keys
to browse the results.

00:01:35.190 --> 00:01:38.190
From this screen you can add
titles to your wish list,

00:01:38.190 --> 00:01:41.500
download them, or access
their details.

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:45.690
Additionally, you may change
the sort order of the book list.

00:01:45.690 --> 00:01:48.970
If you are going to download
or add to your wish list more

00:01:48.970 --> 00:01:54.370 position:56%
than one title from this list, I
recommend you use the advanced view.

00:01:54.370 --> 00:01:59.260
Switch to the advanced view using
the keyboard shortcut control L.

00:01:59.260 --> 00:02:03.640
Then select the titles you wish
to download using the spacebar.

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:06.790
In this example, we are
going to download three books

00:02:06.790 --> 00:02:09.160
